Interface NamedSPILoader.NamedSPI

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Codec, DocValuesFormat, FilterCodec, Lucene3xCodec, Lucene40Codec, Lucene40DocValuesFormat, Lucene40PostingsFormat, Lucene41Codec, Lucene41PostingsFormat, Lucene42Codec, Lucene42DocValuesFormat, Lucene45Codec, Lucene45DocValuesFormat, PerFieldDocValuesFormat, PerFieldPostingsFormat, PostingsFormat
    Enclosing class:

    public static interface NamedSPILoader.NamedSPI
    Interface to support NamedSPILoader.lookup(String) by name.

    Names must be all ascii alphanumeric, and less than 128 characters in length.
